{"id":604,"date":"2023-04-09T18:12:13","date_gmt":"2023-04-09T11:12:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/?page_id=604"},"modified":"2023-04-10T11:29:07","modified_gmt":"2023-04-10T04:29:07","slug":"lao-dong-pho-thong","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/lao-dong-pho-thong\/","title":{"rendered":"Lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1046537033\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1227255447\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\" data-fontsize=\"30\" data-lineheight=\"43\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900;\"><strong>Cung \u1ee9ng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng \u0111a ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 NHANH \u2013 UY T\u00cdN \u2013 CHUY\u00caN NGHI\u1ec6P<\/strong><\/span><\/h1>\n<p>L\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb cung \u1ee9ng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 12 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ngh\u1ec1. Cung \u1ee9ng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/p>\n<p>Cung \u1ee8ng Lao \u0110\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111a ng\u00e0nh \u0111a ngh\u1ec1, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi nhu c\u1ea7u thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cung \u1ee9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c tr\u1ebb em, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0<\/li>\n<li>Cung \u1ee9ng th\u1ee3 tay ngh\u1ec1: C\u01a1 kh\u00ed, nh\u00f4m k\u00ednh, m\u1ed9c, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n l\u1ea1nh \u2026<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng, qu\u00e1n \u0103n, kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung \u1ee9ng c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, d\u00e0y da, may m\u1eb7c, s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u00e1nh k\u1eb9o, \u2026<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung \u1ee9ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trang tr\u1ea1i, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, b\u1ed1c x\u1ebfp, giao h\u00e0ng, ..<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1051096156\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-663373856\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"box has-hover   has-hover box-text-bottom\" >\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-image\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-cover\" style=\"padding-top:57%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<img width=\"650\" height=\"434\" src=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cho-thue-xe-tai-va-boc-xep-650x434-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cho-thue-xe-tai-va-boc-xep-650x434-1.jpg 650w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cho-thue-xe-tai-va-boc-xep-650x434-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cho-thue-xe-tai-va-boc-xep-650x434-1-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-text text-center\" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"box-text-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\n<header class=\"bt_bb_headline bt_bb_font_weight_900 bt_bb_dash_none bt_bb_size_small bt_bb_align_inherit\" data-bt-override-class=\"{}\">\n<h4 class=\"bt_bb_headline_tag\"><span class=\"bt_bb_headline_content\" style=\"color: #ff9900;\">D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 CUNG \u1ee8NG NH\u00c2N S\u1ef0 B\u1ea2O V\u1ec6, B\u1ed0C X\u1ebeP, GIAO H\u00c0NG\u2026<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/header>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_small\" data-bt-override-class=\"null\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_text\">\n<p>Cung \u1ee8ng Lao \u0110\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n b\u1ed1c x\u1ebfp, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, giao h\u00e0ng\u2026chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, si\u00eang n\u0103ng. Th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng v\u00ec kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i..<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111a d\u1ea1ng cho vi\u1ec7c cung \u1ee9ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, chi ph\u00ed ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n<p>Cung \u1ee8ng Lao \u0110\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"tel:0941570444\" target=\"_self\" class=\"button primary box-shadow-3\"  style=\"border-radius:10px;\">\n    <span>li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1579650548\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"box has-hover   has-hover box-text-bottom\" >\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-image\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"\" >\n\t\t\t\t<img width=\"2560\" height=\"1460\" src=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-300x171.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-1024x584.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-150x86.jpg 150w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-768x438.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-1536x876.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/01022013041845_IMG_4124-2048x1168.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-text text-center\" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"box-text-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\n<header class=\"bt_bb_headline bt_bb_font_weight_900 bt_bb_dash_none bt_bb_size_small bt_bb_align_inherit\" data-bt-override-class=\"{}\">\n<h4 class=\"bt_bb_headline_tag\"><span class=\"bt_bb_headline_content\" style=\"color: #ff9900;\">CUNG \u1ee8NG V\u1ec6 SINH C\u00d4NG NGHI\u1ec6P<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/header>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_small\" data-bt-override-class=\"null\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_text\">\n<p>Cung \u1ee8ng Lao \u0110\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1ec7 sinh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 mang t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<p>\u2013 \u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1ec7 sinh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<p>\u2013 Cam k\u1ebft mang t\u1edbi cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 uy t\u00edn, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"tel:0941570444\" target=\"_self\" class=\"button primary\"  style=\"border-radius:10px;\">\n    <span>li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1362215195\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"box has-hover   has-hover box-text-bottom\" >\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-image\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-cover\" style=\"padding-top:57%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/a.jpg\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung \u1ee9ng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/a.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/a-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/a-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/a-150x100.jpg 150w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/a-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-text text-center\" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"box-text-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\n<header class=\"bt_bb_headline bt_bb_font_weight_900 bt_bb_dash_none bt_bb_size_small bt_bb_align_inherit\" data-bt-override-class=\"{}\">\n<h4 class=\"bt_bb_headline_tag\"><span class=\"bt_bb_headline_content\" style=\"color: #ff9900;\">CUNG \u1ee8NG NH\u00c2N VI\u00caN CHO C\u00c1C NG\u00c0NH D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/header>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_small\" data-bt-override-class=\"null\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_text\">\n<p>C\u00e1c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng, kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n\u2026lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 do ngu\u1ed3n lao \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, lao \u0111\u1ed9ng sinh vi\u00ean n\u00ean th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u. Do v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ec3n nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh do gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00e0 lao \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0o ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tay ngh\u1ec1<\/p>\n<p>Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Cung \u1ee8ng Lao \u0110\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u2013 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tuy\u1ec3n nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ngu\u1ed3n lao \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 1 ngu\u1ed3n lao \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi lao \u0111\u1ed9ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi c\u00f3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"tel:0941570444\" target=\"_self\" class=\"button primary\"  style=\"border-radius:10px;\">\n    <span>li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"row\"  id=\"row-1406404050\">\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1150102232\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"box has-hover   has-hover box-text-bottom\" >\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-image\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-cover\" style=\"padding-top:57%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/tho-han-sat-dao-tai-nha-1024x683-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/tho-han-sat-dao-tai-nha-1024x683-1.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/tho-han-sat-dao-tai-nha-1024x683-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/tho-han-sat-dao-tai-nha-1024x683-1-150x100.jpg 150w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/tho-han-sat-dao-tai-nha-1024x683-1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-text text-center\" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"box-text-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\n<header class=\"bt_bb_headline bt_bb_font_weight_900 bt_bb_dash_none bt_bb_size_small bt_bb_align_inherit\" data-bt-override-class=\"{}\">\n<h4 class=\"bt_bb_headline_tag\"><span class=\"bt_bb_headline_content\" style=\"color: #ff9900;\">CUNG \u1ee8NG TH\u1ee2 TAY NGH\u1ec0<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/header>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_small\" data-bt-override-class=\"null\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_text\">\n<p>Cung \u1ee8ng Lao \u0110\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng cung c\u1ea5p ngu\u1ed3n lao \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, th\u1ee3 tay ngh\u1ec1 (K\u1ef9 s\u01b0, th\u1ee3 h\u00e0n, th\u1ee3 l\u1eafp, th\u1ee3 m\u00e1y..) theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p>Lao \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0n h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 ph\u00fat trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f4ng tin l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ngay danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd C\u00f4ng Ty.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"tel:0941570444\" target=\"_self\" class=\"button primary box-shadow-1\"  style=\"border-radius:10px;\">\n    <span>li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-1777314382\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"box has-hover   has-hover box-text-bottom\" >\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-image\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-cover\" style=\"padding-top:57%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<img width=\"800\" height=\"573\" src=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/giup-viec-nha-theo-gio-1-1426.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/giup-viec-nha-theo-gio-1-1426.png 800w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/giup-viec-nha-theo-gio-1-1426-300x215.png 300w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/giup-viec-nha-theo-gio-1-1426-150x107.png 150w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/giup-viec-nha-theo-gio-1-1426-768x550.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-text text-center\" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"box-text-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\n<header class=\"bt_bb_headline bt_bb_font_weight_900 bt_bb_dash_none bt_bb_size_small bt_bb_align_inherit\" data-bt-override-class=\"{}\">\n<h4 class=\"bt_bb_headline_tag\"><span class=\"bt_bb_headline_content\" style=\"color: #ff9900;\">CUNG \u1ee8NG GI\u00daP VI\u1ec6C H\u00c0NH CH\u00cdNH THEO GI\u1edc<\/span><\/h4>\n<\/header>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_small\" data-bt-override-class=\"null\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<div class=\"bt_bb_text\">\n<p>Cung \u1ee8ng Lao \u0110\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng ty chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1ec7 sinh v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1eeda,\u2026 V\u1edbi h\u01a1n 5 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadn t\u00e2m, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e2n h\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng Qu\u00fd Doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng gh\u00e9 th\u0103m v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng.<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"tel:0941570444\" target=\"_self\" class=\"button primary box-shadow-2\"  style=\"border-radius:10px;\">\n    <span>li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-403907360\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t<div class=\"box has-hover   has-hover box-text-bottom\" >\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-image\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-cover\" style=\"padding-top:57%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1600\" height=\"992\" src=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cong-ty-khong-ky-hop-dong-lao-dong-co-bi-phat-khong.jpg\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cong-ty-khong-ky-hop-dong-lao-dong-co-bi-phat-khong.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cong-ty-khong-ky-hop-dong-lao-dong-co-bi-phat-khong-300x186.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cong-ty-khong-ky-hop-dong-lao-dong-co-bi-phat-khong-1024x635.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cong-ty-khong-ky-hop-dong-lao-dong-co-bi-phat-khong-150x93.jpg 150w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cong-ty-khong-ky-hop-dong-lao-dong-co-bi-phat-khong-768x476.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Cong-ty-khong-ky-hop-dong-lao-dong-co-bi-phat-khong-1536x952.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"box-text text-center\" >\n\t\t\t<div class=\"box-text-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\n<div id=\"HEADLINE1034\" class=\"ladi-element ladi-animation\">\n<div id=\"HEADLINE1052\" class=\"ladi-element ladi-animation\">\n<div id=\"HEADLINE1061\" class=\"ladi-element ladi-animation\">\n<div id=\"HEADLINE1070\" class=\"ladi-element ladi-animation\">\n<div id=\"HEADLINE1079\" class=\"ladi-element ladi-animation\">\n<h4 class=\"ladi-headline\"><span style=\"color: #ff9900;\">CUNG C\u1ea4P LAO \u0110\u1ed8NG PH\u1ed4 TH\u00d4NG<\/span><\/h4>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"HEADLINE1080\" class=\"ladi-element ladi-animation\">\n<p class=\"ladi-headline\">Kinh t\u1ebf ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng t\u0103ng cao. Do \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00f4ng ty ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y. Cung \u1ee9ng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin y\u00eau l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c cung c\u1ea5p gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n<a href=\"tel:0941570444\" target=\"_self\" class=\"button primary box-shadow-4\"  style=\"border-radius:10px;\">\n    <span>li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-blank.php","meta":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v20.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng - C\u00d4NG TY TNHH NH\u00c2N L\u1ef0C \u0110\u1ea0I D\u01af\u01a0NG<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/lao-dong-pho-thong\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng - C\u00d4NG TY TNHH NH\u00c2N L\u1ef0C \u0110\u1ea0I D\u01af\u01a0NG\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/cungunglaodongdaiduong.com\/lao-dong-pho-thong\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_n